OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright morning with
OL,6,Fsunny spells turning increasingly
OL,7,Fhazy. Becoming cloudy in the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith a few outbreaks of rain arriving
OL,9,Flater. Winds light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening and
OL,12,Fnight with outbreaks of rain, mostly
OL,13,Flight, but perhaps briefly moderate or
OL,14,Fheavy for a time. Turning drier from
OL,15,Fthe southwest later in the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,18,Fspots of light rain, but some drier,
OL,19,Fbrighter spells developing in the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Outbreaks of rain will then
OL,21,Fspread northeast overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
