OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Ffairly unsettled and changeable few
OL,7,Fdays with a series of showery or
OL,8,Foccasionally more persistent bands of
OL,9,Frain spreading up from the southwest
